{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"n0j2ootma2fifoxdm24zs2e","title":"Binding Components","desc":"","updated":1687542248408,"created":1687541870116,"custom":{},"fname":"web-components.high-level-solutions.lit.binding-components","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"c8c41efefddce01659f9a2349aeefc91","links":[{"from":{"fname":"web-components.high-level-solutions.lit","id":"ik9twe6vf70yht7mt79j88t","vaultName":"docs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":20,"offset":2024},"end":{"line":59,"column":121,"offset":2125},"indent":[]},"value":"web-components.high-level-solutions.lit.binding-components"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"ik9twe6vf70yht7mt79j88t","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"binding-components\">Binding Components<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#binding-components\"></a></h1>\n<p>Lit puede usarse para interactuar con otros Web Components existentes en nuestras aplicaciones. En el ejemplo anterior creamos de forma imperativa una referencia y un event listener para nuestro dropdown. </p>\n<p>Primero crearemos un componente raiz en el nivel mas alto.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">//x-app.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">LitElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> html<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lit'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>property<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lit/decorators.js'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dropdown'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XApp</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LitElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span> html<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token html language-html\">\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>x-dropdown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        Hello from Lit!\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>x-dropdown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'x-app'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">XApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Con este componente podemos usar el binding declarativo de Lit para setear propiedades y escuchar a eventos</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">//x-app.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">LitElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> html<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lit'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>property<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lit/decorators.js'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dropdown'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XApp</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LitElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span> html<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token html language-html\">\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>x-dropdown</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">@visibleChange</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        Hello from Lit!\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>x-dropdown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token console class-name\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'x-app'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">XApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Usamos el <code>@</code> para escuchar al evento. Esto funciona no solo con eventos nativos del DOM sino tambien con eventos custom como <code>visibleChange</code>. Podemos hacer lo mismo con las propiedades:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">//x-app.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">LitElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> html<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lit'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>property<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lit/decorators.js'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dropdown'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XApp</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LitElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">customTitle</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Custom Title!'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span> html<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token html language-html\">\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>x-dropdown</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">@visibleChange</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">.title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">customTitle</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        Hello from Lit!\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>x-dropdown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token console class-name\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'x-app'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">XApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>En lit usamos el <code>.</code> para bindear propiedades.</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/ik9twe6vf70yht7mt79j88t\">Lit</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1687570355610,"created":1687478467553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"503e0f736c7c1d0c26ed87839ccd08a9","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"https://webcomponent.dev/","alias":"Cory Rylan","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":94,"offset":117},"end":{"line":4,"column":134,"offset":157},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"https://webcomponent.dev/"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.Apis.custom-elements","alias":"Custom Elements","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":227},"end":{"line":9,"column":60,"offset":284},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.Apis.custom-elements"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.Apis.shadow-dom","alias":"Shadow Dow","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":287},"end":{"line":10,"column":49,"offset":333},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.Apis.shadow-dom"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.Apis.content-slot","alias":"Content Slot","position":{"start":{"line"